	<!-- Introduction -->
	<purpose>
This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the representation of use or design cases of product or process data in a family of products offered to market, 
 these use or design cases being defined with Boolean combinations of product characteristics.
 </purpose>
	<!-- Items in scope -->
	<inscope>
		<li>characterization of a use case of product or process data with a Boolean combinations of product characteristics;</li>
		<li>characterization of a design case of product or process data with a Boolean combinations of product characteristics;</li>
		<li>assignment of date-based effectivity to a use case;</li>
		<li>assignment of a use case to a part occurrence.</li>
	</inscope>
